title: Patriot Games
description:
Mina and former NFL offensive lineman Geoff Schwartz look ahead to the top games in Week 10 of the NFL season including Browns-Patriots, Seahawks-Packers, and Chiefs-Raiders. Plus, Mina's poor clock management once again puts her in the hot seat for Dinks and Dunks.
